_sText:
De_rats_garage_b7
All NEW screenshots!!

::UPDATE::
b7 updates
fixed falling areas on the toolbox and the waterheater.
fixed bombsite A bomb effects against the wall
added ladders to the rafters from the workbench and the entertainment center
added a hole from the left side of the entertainment center to the middle shelf
added a dustpan next to the trashcan for coverfire when rushing

b6 updates
Fixed two areas where you could fall and not get out.
The tablesaw works and is started/stopped by a button. This will hurt and hurl players.
Bombsite A blows a hole in the walls of the fridge and house.
Bombsite B blows the garage door out onto the car.
::::::::


Bombsites are:
A: Fridge, middle shelf
B: Garage door motor


Ts start outside and need to make it inside and past the CTs to get to A or take the rafters and plant at B.  CTs start in the kitchen and need to defend the cheese in the fridge and the garage door motor in the rafters.


Its been a while since my last map but I think you will like this one.  It has been tested through a few versions on KrackHouse.net servers.  Come visit us at 69.28.221.214:27015 on our GunGame Rats server or 66.55.154.62:27015 on our Regular Rats server.

Textures and models are inserted into the BSP.  Models were made by Reaper (THANKS).
